_:N13a5d3e7e89a4e658bffb69cf1ce9194 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Baroness Chapman was appointed Minister of State (International Development and Africa) in the Foreign, Commonwealth &amp; Development Office in September 2025.</p>\n\n<p>Baroness Chapman has held previous senior roles in the Foreign, Commonwealth &amp; Development Office. On 28 February 2025 she was appointed Minister of State (International Development, Latin America and Caribbean).</p>\n\n<p>Before that she was Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State at the Foreign, Commonwealth and Development Office between 18 July 2024 and 28 February 2025.</p>\n\n<div role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Information\" class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n  <p>Follow Baroness Chapman on X: <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://x.com/jennychapman\">@JennyChapman</a>.</p>\n</div>\n" .
